# Ticket ID: TICKET-020

## Issue Title
User unable to connect to VPN

## Description
Remote user unable to establish VPN connection.

## User Reported Problem
VPN authentication failed.

## Initial Checks (L1)
- Verified internet connectivity
- Checked VPN client status

## Troubleshooting Performed
- Verified user credentials
- Checked VPN account validity
- Reset VPN credentials

## Root Cause
Expired VPN credentials.

## Resolution
Credentials renewed and VPN access restored.

## Status
Resolved at L1 level

## SLA Impact
Resolved within SLA

## Learning
Authentication issues are common VPN failures.
